Title: ensembl_transcript_lengths_GCcontent
Description: A dataset containing the transcript lengths and GC content for each human ensembl gene

Title: mouse_to_human_homologs
Description: A dataset containing the MGI and HGNC symbols, Human and Mouse Entrez and Ensembl gene IDs for all human orthologs for mouse genes. Whenin the mouse genes are defined based on a list of all MGI markers from the MGI website

Title: all_mgi_wtEnsembl
Description: A dataset containing all MGI symbols in first column, then ensembl_gene_id in second column

Title: all_mgi
Description: A dataset containing all MGI symbols

Title: all_hgnc_wtEnsembl
Description: A dataset containing all HGNC symbols in first column, then ensembl_gene_id in second column

Title: all_hgnc
Description: A dataset containing all HGNC symbols

Title: example_genelist
Description: A list of genes genetically associated with Alzheimer's disease

Title: tt_alzh
Description: A list of genes found to be differentially expressed in the BA46 in Alzheimer's disease.

Title: tt_alzh_BA36
Description: A list of genes found to be differentially expressed in the BA36 in Alzheimer's disease.

Title: tt_alzh_BA44
Description: A list of genes found to be differentially expressed in the BA44 in Alzheimer's disease.

Title: ctd
Description: The genes from Karolinska cortex/hippocampus and hypothalamus single cell transcriptome datasets

Title: rbfox_genes
Description: Rbfox binding genes from HITS-CLIP and Integrative Modeling Define the Rbfox Splicing-Regulatory Network Linked to Brain Development and Autism.

Title: alzh_gwas_top100
Description: Alzheimers disease top100 GWAS genes generated by MAGMA using the iGAP summary statistics
